{"tid":1419740,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"咪撚再分化前線，你地憑乜話佢地？","createTime":"2019-08-06T02:27:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T10:50:20.000Z","uid":59522,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b5ef715cf94ec91565f70cdd6ece6d27a4b89995","tid":1419740,"uid":59522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:27:58.000Z","msg":"清場前hold住條戰線俾後面走既係佢地<br />\n推進運動既都係佢地<br />\n打撚走啲黑社會又係佢地<br />\n食催淚最撚多既絕對係佢地<br />\n俾狗捉既都係佢地<br />\n<br />\n其實前線大可以一放tg就即跑唔救火<br />\n佢地咁落力為乜？自己諗下啦如果你有腦既話<br />\n<br />\n仲有！前線既決定你都可以參與提出意見<br />\n只要你係佢地附近一定知會開會，唔開會你講就有人應<br />\n咁你唔撚去前線同佢地講即係<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">有票你唔撚投有選民資格你又唔撚登記</span></span></strong><br />\n咁你上連登屌佢地做錯有撚屎用啊？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一個少一個</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">得把口個班係咪會行上前線做返一撚樣既事補返佢地個位？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔係既就收嗲咪撚再搞分化，你無資格<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">絕不分化，永不割蓆</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aaaacc3de25dd24906bebbe8eaca9d07c01ca0d","tid":1419740,"uid":59522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:35:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d4f6c0c8a09e7f01fe0279a10a04facf4f4a022","tid":1419740,"uid":59522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:39:03.000Z","msg":"話知係唔係P牌狗，咁樣開post對佢地既都抵屌，醒下啦"},{"pid":"3867421d88830cca50e62e1cdec364b7257f4e8e","tid":1419740,"uid":59522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:50:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}